Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:35.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米 克拉克森的职业生涯要告一段落...\N{\fs90}for motoring presenter Jeremy Clarkson...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,...很遗憾\N{\fs90}...and said that it's with deep regret
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:41.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,高层决定 对他不予以复职\N{\fs90}the decision had been taken not to renew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:25.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,预计今日天气晴朗\N{\fs90}forecast plenty of sunshine through today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:27.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,正常季节温度\N{\fs90}with seasonal temperatures.
