Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.67,0:44:08.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,看到没 完全没有转向不足\N{\fs90}See what I mean? No understeer at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.86,0:44:10.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,这破赛道比我家的车道还窄\N{\fs90}Damn tracks are narrower than my driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.98,0:44:13.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是因为你家车道上停着台怪物卡车\N{\fs90}Yeah, that's 'cause it doesn't have a monster truck on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.81,0:44:17.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,真想知道谁把这玩意搞出来的\N{\fs90}Wonder which one of them came up with this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.65,0:44:20.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,那个高个子 小矮子 还是留着娘娘腔头发的\N{\fs90}The tall one? The short one? Or the one with the girly hair?
