Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.89,0:44:39.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个直角弯\N{\fs90}This is a 90-left,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.67,0:44:41.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,新铺的柏油 但抓地力不错\N{\fs90}new Tarmac but it held it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.54,0:44:44.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,绵羊坡上还有个直角弯\N{\fs90}One more 90-left to go through Field Of Sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.65,0:44:47.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,漂亮的过弯 冲线\N{\fs90}And he's done it well. And across the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.45,0:44:54.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,处女秀 真的很不错\N{\fs90}First one. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.15,0:44:55.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,他很优秀\N{\fs90}He's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.69,0:44:58.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,他既会左转也会右转 真厉害\N{\fs90}He's great going left and right. Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.69,0:45:00.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了避免这辆M2\N{\fs90}To make sure that the M2-
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.53,0:45:03.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,在圈速榜上孤单一人\N{\fs90}that wasn't on the lap board all by itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.46,0:45:06.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们把这个美国人扔进了其他标杆车里\N{\fs90}we got the American to put other benchmark cars-
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.50,0:45:10.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们叫标杆车型 他叫我党车型\N{\fs90}we call them benchmark cars, he calls them communist-
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.67,0:45:12.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,来跑几圈 看看他们到底几斤几两\N{\fs90}around the track, to see what's what.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.71,0:45:14.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,有迈凯伦 奥迪 等等\N{\fs90}McLaren, Audi and so forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.61,0:45:16.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,等下 我在之前片子里\N{\fs90}Hang on a minute. We saw a Ferrari 488
