Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.31,0:45:19.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么它没上榜\N{\fs90}Why isn't that on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.51,0:45:21.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为法拉利不让我们测圈速\N{\fs90}Because Ferrari wouldn't let us time it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.72,0:45:23.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-不让测  -不让\N{\fs90}- Wouldn't let us? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.58,0:45:26.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以说 法拉利拉法不能上路\N{\fs90}So the Ferrari LaFerrari can't go on the road
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.32,0:45:28.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,-没有纯电模式 -是的\N{\fs90}- or run on electric only? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.51,0:45:30.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后488还不能来测圈速\N{\fs90}And the 488 can't do a timed lap?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.62,0:45:33.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,法拉利那边总是很难交涉\N{\fs90}Ferrari are quite tricky to deal with from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.54,0:45:36.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们别去管他了 来看看\N{\fs90}Let's just put it that way and move on. It's time to see
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.43,0:45:39.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,M2在榜上能排在哪\N{\fs90}where the M2 goes on that board.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.03,0:45:41.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,拭目以待 把圈速放上来\N{\fs90}Let's have a look. Let's put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.60,0:45:43.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢 -哈哈\N{\fs90}- Oh! - Ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.84,0:45:45.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,哇 哇\N{\fs90}Wow! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.47,0:45:49.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我觉得这是他们造过最好的M\N{\fs90}"I think it's the best M car they've ever made."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.94,0:45:52.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可不是我说的\N{\fs90}Not my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.01,0:45:55.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,虽然这车最慢 我却独钟情于它\N{\fs90}"I prefer it to all the others that are quicker than it."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.38,0:45:58.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是 但这只是 -这车是最佳选择\N{\fs90}- Yes, it's- - The one you should have,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.32,0:46:00.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你想要一辆最慢的M系的话\N{\fs90}if you want one that's slower than all the other M cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.62,0:46:03.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,没这么惨 仅仅慢了两秒-\N{\fs90}It's better. It's only two seconds-
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.29,0:46:05.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,-至少比思域快 -确实\N{\fs90}- It's quicker than a Civic. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.93,0:46:07.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,但它还是慢过\N{\fs90}But it's slower than-
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.53,0:46:09.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你把M车型列出来 选一辆车\N{\fs90}If you had a choice of M cars, lined them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.33,0:46:11.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后说 我想要最快的 那绝对不是这辆了\N{\fs90}and said, "I'd like the fastest", it wouldn't be that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.83,0:46:15.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,-闭嘴 -在每一点上都更好\N{\fs90}- Shut up. - Better in every single way?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.23,0:46:17.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,-那是你说的 -我不管 你开过M2吗\N{\fs90}- You said that. - I don't care. Have you driven one?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.74,0:46:20.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,-开过-简直是惊世骇俗\N{\fs90}- I have. - It's fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.67,0:46:23.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,这真是辆好车 真的是\N{\fs90}It's a brilliant car. It really honestly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.34,0:46:26.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜 我们不能带着赛道环游世界\N{\fs90}It's a shame we can't take the track round the world with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.50,0:46:29.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,真要这样 我们就能邀请明星来开\N{\fs90}Because if we did, we could invite celebrities to drive round it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.62,0:46:31.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,还能弄个圈速榜\N{\fs90}and we could keep a score sheet
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.65,0:46:33.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,看看谁最快\N{\fs90}of who was the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.89,0:46:37.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢这主意\N{\fs90}No, I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.52,0:46:39.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我也不喜欢\N{\fs90}I don't like it, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.09,0:46:41.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不信它能火啊 -没人爱看这个\N{\fs90}- I don't think it would work. - Nobody wants to watch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.88,0:46:44.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,真不信 不管怎么样 我有更好的主意\N{\fs90}I'm not sure that they do. Anyway, we've got a better idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.63,0:46:46.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的明星环节\N{\fs90}Okay, for our celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.63,0:46:49.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,就叫它 明星脑碰脑\N{\fs90}We're calling it Celebrity Brain Crash,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.37,0:46:52.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们也做了个小片头\N{\fs90}and we had a sting made for that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.48,0:47:02.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了\N{\fs90}That is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.52,0:47:04.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不想用这个\N{\fs90}I don't like to use this...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.05,0:47:10.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,实在太糟了\N{\fs90}It's just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.42,0:47:14.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁会说 我要去看亚马逊的新汽车节目\N{\fs90}Who is gonna say, "I'm gonna watch that new Amazon car show.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.43,0:47:17.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,里面亨利八世的脑袋炸了\N{\fs90}Henry VIII's head explodes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.13,0:47:20.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,为什么布拉德皮特的头在冒烟\N{\fs90}Why is there smoke coming out of Brad Pitt's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.64,0:47:23.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是想表达什么\N{\fs90}What are we trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.14,0:47:25.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 我们不是 -我们不是这意思\N{\fs90}- No, we're not. - No, we're not saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.41,0:47:28.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,不是这个意思\N{\fs90}Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.31,0:47:30.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个片头糟透了\N{\fs90}That is a terrible sting,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.14,0:47:33.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这仪器真不错\N{\fs90}but the machine itself isn't terrible at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.20,0:47:36.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是用来测量人体灵活度\N{\fs90}It's used to measure somebody's mental agility,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.22,0:47:38.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,观测能力\N{\fs90}their observational skills
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.02,0:47:40.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,以及多线程操作能力\N{\fs90}and their ability to multi-task.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.40,0:47:42.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,实际上它是基于\N{\fs90}It's actually based on a machine
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.62,0:47:44.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,给要加入皇家空军\N{\fs90}that's used to test fighter pilots
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.74,0:47:46.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,战斗机飞行员测试的仪器\N{\fs90}who want to join the Royal Air Force
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.79,0:47:49.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都知道 这是全世界\N{\fs90}which, as we all know, is the finest and greatest air force
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.73,0:47:52.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,最好的空军了\N{\fs90}in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.00,0:47:56.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们这喝倒彩什么意思\N{\fs90}What do you mean, "Boo"? What do you mean, "Boo"? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.64,0:47:59.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,要是这样 你们每次出状况为什么还要我们帮忙\N{\fs90}If that was true, we wouldn't have to help you every time you get in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.28,0:48:10.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我先坐下忍着\N{\fs90}I'll hold myself back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.12,0:48:13.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,等等 你们怎么抱怨都行\N{\fs90}Now, hold on. You lot can grumble as much as you like,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.92,0:48:16.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,反正这节目是由我们英国人来剪辑\N{\fs90}but we edit this show and we're British,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.92,0:48:19.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以这肯定会被切的\N{\fs90}so you'll just get cut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.53,0:48:22.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都同意\N{\fs90}We're all in agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.06,0:48:26.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,皇家空军就是比美国空军好\N{\fs90}That the Royal Air Force is better than the US Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.30,0:48:29.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,美利坚 美利坚 美利坚\N{\fs90}USA! USA! USA!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.90,0:48:32.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都同意\N{\fs90}We're all in agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.30,0:48:35.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,皇家空军就是比美国空军好\N{\fs90}the Royal Air Force is better than all the other air forces in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.91,0:48:40.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在都同意\N{\fs90}We're all now in agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.00,0:48:43.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,皇家空军是\N{\fs90}The Royal Air Force is-
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.02,0:48:45.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,世界上最棒的\N{\fs90}is the best air force in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.09,0:48:50.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都同意 皇家空军还是比较厉害的\N{\fs90}So we're all in agreement the Royal Air Force is quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.59,0:48:53.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,差不多就行了\N{\fs90}That will do. That will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.49,0:48:57.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们回到明星脑碰脑\N{\fs90}So let's get back to Celebrity Brain Crash
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.23,0:48:59.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,看看我们第一位嘉宾\N{\fs90}and meet our first-ever guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.17,0:49:00.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,在其他节目里\N{\fs90}Normally on other shows,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.97,0:49:03.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,嘉宾一般都会从亮闪闪的幕布里走出\N{\fs90}the guest will come through a sparkly curtain,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.67,0:49:06.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,挥手致意 然后坐下 这里不一样\N{\fs90}wave a bit and then sit down, but not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.92,0:49:10.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 我们的嘉宾入场可正式了\N{\fs90}Oh, yes, our guests make a proper arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.12,0:49:13.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样 有请今晚的嘉宾\N{\fs90}And on that note, let's meet tonight's star.
