Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.79,0:49:20.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,除了单身日记\N{\fs90}apart from Bridget Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.82,0:49:22.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,他就是主演啊\N{\fs90}No, he was Bridget Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.82,0:49:25.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,是么 -不\N{\fs90}- Was he? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.06,0:49:27.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,不过没关系 他参演过谍影重重\N{\fs90}But it doesn't matter. He was in the Bourne films.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.03,0:49:29.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,还演过碟中谍\N{\fs90}He was in the Mission Impossible films,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.73,0:49:31.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有复仇者联盟\N{\fs90}the Avengers films,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.06,0:49:34.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在 他在我们头顶3000米的高空盘旋\N{\fs90}and right now he is 10.000 feet above us,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.17,0:49:36.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,等着进行华丽的入场\N{\fs90}waiting to make one hell of an entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.95,0:49:39.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 杰瑞米 雷纳\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, Jeremy Renner!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.94,0:49:45.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,他在那 就这架飞机\N{\fs90}There he is. There he is, that's his plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.88,0:49:52.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fs90}Hold on, everybody. Here he comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.92,0:49:55.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,他准备跳了\N{\fs90}He is ready to jump.
