Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.32,0:50:00.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,他准备跳了 他来了\N{\fs90}He is ready to jump. And there he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.60,0:50:02.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,能看他自己做特技\N{\fs90}That is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.09,0:50:03.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,简直神奇啊\N{\fs90}to see him doing his own stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.90,0:50:07.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 而且他看上去真帅\N{\fs90}Yeah, I know. And he is looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.47,0:50:09.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,等他到了\N{\fs90}When he gets here,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.50,0:50:12.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想和他聊聊谍影重重4\N{\fs90}I do want to talk to him about that Bourne Legacy film.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.24,0:50:14.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,一是 揍肖恩 雅克博森什么感觉\N{\fs90}what it was like to punch Shane Jacobson.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.98,0:50:17.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,二是 等等\N{\fs90}And, B... Ooh, hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.01,0:50:21.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,他开伞好晚啊\N{\fs90}He's leaving this terribly late.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.90,0:50:43.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs90}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.07,0:50:45.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是不是就意味着他来不了了\N{\fs90}Does that mean he's not coming on, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.41,0:50:48.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 詹姆斯 他来不了了\N{\fs90}No, James, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.31,0:50:51.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,没关系 我们已经预料到有类似的情况了\N{\fs90}It's okay, though. We anticipated this sort of thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.65,0:50:53.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们有一个替补嘉宾\N{\fs90}so we got a back-up guest ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.68,0:50:55.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,额\N{\fs90}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.68,0:50:58.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,他出演过秘密特工\N{\fs90}He was in Man From Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.05,0:51:01.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,出演过独行侠\N{\fs90}He was in Lone Ranger. He was both twins
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.52,0:51:03.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,在社交网络里同时扮演了双胞胎\N{\fs90}in The Social Network.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.26,0:51:06.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,他最新出演的电影叫做夜行动物\N{\fs90}And his new film is called Nocturnal Animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.06,0:51:08.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,很抱歉我们没有时间\N{\fs90}We haven't had time, unfortunately,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.06,0:51:09.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,来安排一个戏剧性的入场\N{\fs90}to organize a dramatic entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.00,0:51:12.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我希望各位还是欢迎他的到来\N{\fs90}but I hope you'll give him a warm welcome nevertheless.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.87,0:51:15.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 有请 艾米 汉莫\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, Armie Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.47,0:51:18.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,他那里\N{\fs90}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.44,0:51:21.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦 我的\N{\fs90}Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.34,0:51:23.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs90}Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.18,0:51:24.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是一条蛇么\N{\fs90}Is that a snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.98,0:51:26.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的— 是条响尾蛇\N{\fs90}- It's a snake. - That's a rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.91,0:51:28.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的— 是啊\N{\fs90}- Is it? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.88,0:51:31.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,他在垂死挣扎 各位 请安静\N{\fs90}He's being killed. Quiet, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.82,0:51:33.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,请安静一下\N{\fs90}Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.82,0:51:35.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们真的什么都做不了\N{\fs90}There's literally nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.89,0:51:37.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,他离我们好远啊\N{\fs90}He's yards away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.89,0:51:39.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,但毒蛇是一群一群的\N{\fs90}Snakes are like herds of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.56,0:51:42.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们群体打猎 -他们是群居动物\N{\fs90}- They hunt in packs. - Yeah, they're pack animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.30,0:51:45.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是不是说 他也进不来了\N{\fs90}Does that mean he's not coming on either?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.03,0:51:48.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 詹姆斯 他在痛苦的抽搐中死去\N{\fs90}No, James, he's finished writhing around in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.34,0:51:50.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在他死翘翘了\N{\fs90}And now he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.39,0:51:52.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他也进不来了\N{\fs90}So that is a no.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.41,0:51:54.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 额\N{\fs90}Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.21,0:51:56.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,也许我们的观众里有一些名人呢\N{\fs90}maybe there's somebody famous in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.81,0:51:58.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,不太可能吧\N{\fs90}That's unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.78,0:52:01.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,怎么不可能 你们知道 卡罗尔·沃德曼 么\N{\fs90}No. Seriously, you know Carol Vorderman?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.25,0:52:03.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,她今早给我打电话说她在附近看航展\N{\fs90}She rang me this morning from an air show nearby
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.85,0:52:06.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,还问能不能来参加节目\N{\fs90}and said, can she come to the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.85,0:52:08.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道你们不知道卡罗尔 沃德曼是谁\N{\fs90}I know you don't know who Carol Vorderman is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.89,0:52:11.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,她在英国可是红得发紫啊\N{\fs90}She's a huge, huge, huge star in the UK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.39,0:52:13.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,她从一档叫做Countdown的节目里发迹\N{\fs90}She started out on a program called Countdown
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.43,0:52:15.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,在剧中 将自己打造成无比聪慧\N{\fs90}and established herself as being unbelievably brilliant,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.73,0:52:17.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,美轮美奂的数学家\N{\fs90}a fantastic mathematician
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.73,0:52:20.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,此外还漂亮\N{\fs90}and very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.42,0:52:23.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,是呢  她也死了\N{\fs90}Yes, she's also dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.07,0:52:24.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,嘛\N{\fs90}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.57,0:52:28.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,啥 -她死了\N{\fs90}- What? - She's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.37,0:52:31.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是什么情况啊 -不知道 我又不学病理的\N{\fs90}- How did that happen? - I don't know. I'm not a pathologist!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.18,0:52:33.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是她像这样就死了\N{\fs90}But she's dead is what she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.81,0:52:36.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,真的么 -是啊\N{\fs90}- Seriously? - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.33,0:52:38.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊 -出事了吧\N{\fs90}- Christ. - Problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.75,0:52:41.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们现在应该怎么办呢\N{\fs90}What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.12,0:52:42.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,额\N{\fs90}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.35,0:52:44.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊 看看这外面 就像个\N{\fs90}Jesus, look at that out there. It's like a-
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.76,0:52:46.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,简直横尸遍野啊\N{\fs90}It's just littered with corpses.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.83,0:52:52.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,弟兄们 我觉得这环节没有存在必要了\N{\fs90}Lads, I don't think this bit is working.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.37,0:52:53.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们就把\N{\fs90}Let's drop
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.73,0:52:56.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,明星脑碰脑 这周的给切了吧\N{\fs90}Celebrity Brain Crash this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.07,0:52:58.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,下周去了南非再搞\N{\fs90}We'll do it again in South Africa next week,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.19,0:53:00.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,等下周 大家就把这事给忘了\N{\fs90}and I think people will have forgotten all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.27,0:53:02.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,不会吧 -我觉得他们会的\N{\fs90}- They might not. - I think they will.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.01,0:53:05.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们把这段跳过去吧 这些事情从来没发生过对吧\N{\fs90}We'll just skip over it now. It's not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.48,0:53:07.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 因为我们要回到车上来\N{\fs90}That's okay, 'cause we can back to the cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.82,0:53:10.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 继续\N{\fs90}Yes! Moving on!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.18,0:53:14.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,别看 -对 别看\N{\fs90}- Don't look. - Yes, don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.62,0:53:15.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,这周呢\N{\fs90}This week-
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.96,0:53:18.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,这周我们要在新世代混动超跑中找出\N{\fs90}This week we are trying to find out
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.26,0:53:21.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们中哪台是最好的\N{\fs90}which of the new breed of hybrid hypercars is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.06,0:53:23.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 第一天我们在葡萄牙赛道上\N{\fs90}Yes. On day one at the track in Portugal,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.40,0:53:27.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们发现迈凯伦P1是一个神经质\N{\fs90}we established that the McLaren P1 is a mentalist,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.07,0:53:30.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,保时捷918是个不错的送奶车\N{\fs90}that the Porsche 918 is a very good milk float,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.67,0:53:33.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,法拉利拉法什么都干不了\N{\fs90}and that the Ferrari LaFerrari can do nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.84,0:53:37.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,有些话是真的\N{\fs90}Some of that is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.44,0:53:39.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是 现在是第二天\N{\fs90}But now, day two.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.16,0:53:52.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们将寰宇中最热血澎湃的\N{\fs90}We began by lining up
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.12,0:53:54.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,三辆速度机器依次排开\N{\fs90}the three most exciting cars on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.90,0:53:58.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,准备进行这个时代的巅峰之战\N{\fs90}for the drag race of all drag races.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.51,0:54:16.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,自然而然 这就意味着要打开弹射起步了\N{\fs90}Naturally, this meant engaging launch control,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.55,0:54:20.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,在迈凯伦里 大约需要2周\N{\fs90}which in the McLaren takes about a fortnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.60,0:54:24.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要把驾驶模式调节到赛道模式\N{\fs90}I have to have the drive tray in track mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.62,0:54:26.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,空气动力学模块调节到运动\N{\fs90}the aero package in sport mode,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.86,0:54:28.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,在这个模式下 车辆后部会降低\N{\fs90}so that the rear end squats
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.16,0:54:30.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,当我起步的时候回给我更多的抓地力\N{\fs90}when I set off and gives me more traction.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.13,0:54:33.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还需要将DRS按钮用我的大拇指按住\N{\fs90}I have to have the DRS button pressed with my thumb
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.37,0:54:36.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,让尾翼变得水平以极大减小迎面的空气阻力\N{\fs90}to keep the rear wing open which reduces drag obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.95,0:54:40.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,在保时捷里开弹射 左脚踩刹车 猛踩\N{\fs90}Launch control in the Porsche, left foot on the brake hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.51,0:54:42.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,右脚踩油门 猛踩\N{\fs90}Right foot on the throttle hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.51,0:54:44.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,绿灯一亮 左脚一抬 叮\N{\fs90}Light goes green, left foot off brake. Pa-ching!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.88,0:54:47.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,持续按住弹射起步按钮2秒钟\N{\fs90}Launch button, press for two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.25,0:54:49.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,左脚踩刹车 右脚踩油门\N{\fs90}Left foot on brake. Right foot on throttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.88,0:54:52.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,按下弹射起步 狠踩油门\N{\fs90}Press launch control, mash the throttle,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.60,0:54:55.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,四秒内松开刹车\N{\fs90}within four seconds release the brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.58,0:54:58.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,三秒钟后 我将达到最大增压值\N{\fs90}Three seconds later, I have full boost,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.29,0:55:00.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,并且在三秒钟内我必须起步\N{\fs90}and I have to set off within three seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.96,0:55:03.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,否则的话整个系统将取消弹射状态\N{\fs90}or the entire system disengages.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.36,0:55:06.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,我肯定会失败的\N{\fs90}I'm going to get this wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.13,0:55:08.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,通知你们一下\N{\fs90}Just so you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.13,0:55:10.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的准备工作太多了\N{\fs90}I've got a lot to do in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.90,0:55:39.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我没准备好\N{\fs90}I wasn't ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.66,0:55:42.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,天啊 那辆拉法真快\N{\fs90}Oh, my God! That is quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.31,0:55:50.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,亲娘啊 看到了么\N{\fs90}Holy mother! Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.48,0:55:53.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,我* 天啊\N{\fs90}- me! - Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.08,0:55:55.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,到处乱窜\N{\fs90}It's all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.95,0:56:03.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,既然大家都心知肚明是我按错了按钮\N{\fs90}Since it was clear I'd got all my buttons wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.59,0:56:06.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们也都同意再赛一轮\N{\fs90}the chaps agreed to another run.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.34,0:56:08.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,情况报告 增压还没好\N{\fs90}Sit rep, the lights went green
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.76,0:56:11.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,灯就变绿了\N{\fs90}before the boost was ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.10,0:56:13.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,我还按住了DRS按钮\N{\fs90}and I had the DRS button still pressed
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.27,0:56:15.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以到最后 我没了下压力\N{\fs90}when I got to the end, which meant I had no downforce,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.97,0:56:19.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,结果就是 吓出了翔了\N{\fs90}which meant- Well, poo came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.14,0:56:23.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,这次 我要加大下压力\N{\fs90}This time I'm gonna do it with more drag,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.21,0:56:25.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,虽然会慢些 但是刹车的时候\N{\fs90}which will slow me down, but I will be able to stop
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.85,0:56:27.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,我才没有生命危险\N{\fs90}without killing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.95,0:56:35.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,KERS系统充电完成\N{\fs90}KERS system charged. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.69,0:56:42.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,增压中\N{\fs90}Boost building.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.86,0:56:47.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,3 2\N{\fs90}Three, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.97,0:56:53.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,出发了 神起步啊\N{\fs90}And we are away! What a start!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.81,0:56:58.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,保时捷后来居上了\N{\fs90}The Porsche has got off to a flyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.71,0:57:01.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊 我的蛋\N{\fs90}Oh, balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.71,0:57:03.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,180 190 200 210\N{\fs90}180, 190, 210.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.19,0:57:09.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,230公里每小时\N{\fs90}230 kilometers an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.69,0:57:17.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这没发挥好\N{\fs90}That wasn't very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.46,0:57:20.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为詹姆斯不知怎么搞砸了\N{\fs90}Because James had somehow messed up that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.73,0:57:23.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且这测试的重点在车\N{\fs90}and because this test was about the cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.20,0:57:25.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们决定再来一次\N{\fs90}we decided to go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.84,0:57:32.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是个火箭\N{\fs90}It's a rocket ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.01,0:57:36.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了大英帝国\N{\fs90}For England!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.75,0:57:39.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,不要啊\N{\fs90}No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.22,0:57:47.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都赢过一次了\N{\fs90}Okay, we have all three won this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.13,0:57:53.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了最终确定\N{\fs90}Determined to find a definitive
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.05,0:57:55.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,一二三的排名\N{\fs90}one-two-three finishing order,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.94,0:57:57.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们又跑了一次\N{\fs90}we ran again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.71,0:58:06.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,两位 这又是一个完全不同的结果\N{\fs90}Another totally different result there, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.88,0:58:09.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,又一次\N{\fs90}And again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.45,0:58:16.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,又是个不同的结果\N{\fs90}That's a different result again.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.29,0:58:18.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,又一次\N{\fs90}And again?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.60,0:58:25.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,至此 我们决定\N{\fs90}At this point, we decided to call
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.90,0:58:27.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,不再继续下去了\N{\fs90}a halt to proceedings,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.43,0:58:32.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为我们得出了一个科学结论\N{\fs90}because we had reached a scientific conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.10,0:58:35.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,原来这和你买哪辆没关系\N{\fs90}It turns out it doesn't really matter which car you buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.58,0:58:37.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,主要是鞋的问题\N{\fs90}it all depends on your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.56,0:58:39.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家看 这是一双TOD乐福鞋\N{\fs90}Now, this is a TOD loafer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.48,0:58:42.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,轻微的磨损 能够让起步的瞬间\N{\fs90}Slightly worn to get a crisper jump
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.55,0:58:44.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,松刹车的动作更加干脆直接\N{\fs90}off the brake pedal, and it's immediate.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.75,0:58:47.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,他的是匡威 鞋底的填充物比我想象还厚\N{\fs90}- This is a Converse. - There's more sponge in there than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.72,0:58:50.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,你看阿迪也是 他们造鞋的时候也没考虑过这个问题\N{\fs90}See, Adidas, they weren't thinking that through.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.66,0:58:53.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以在你抬脚的时候就已经损失了一毫秒\N{\fs90}- So, as you lift your foot up- - It's a millisecond.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.86,0:58:55.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,无论是你有KERS\N{\fs90}I know you've got KERS,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.19,0:58:56.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,你有6.3升V12引擎\N{\fs90}I know you've got a 6.3-litre V12,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.76,0:58:59.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有出色的弹射启动\N{\fs90}and I know that launch control system is amazing,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.37,0:59:00.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,最终都被\N{\fs90}but it's all let down
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.73,0:59:02.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的阿迪达斯鞋给耽误了\N{\fs90}by the sponginess of the Adidas shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.70,0:59:04.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以车和鞋应该配套卖\N{\fs90}So they should sell you the car and the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.94,0:59:07.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,不止 首先你得有合适的鞋 然后还要磨合一段时间\N{\fs90}No, have you got the correct shoes and have you worn them in?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.51,0:59:09.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 新鞋的话 不好意思各位\N{\fs90}- Exactly. - Fresh shoes, lads.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.51,0:59:13.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,我需要 你需要磨一下才行\N{\fs90}- I just need to- - You need to skid about. There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.75,0:59:16.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,解决了这个问题之后\N{\fs90}With that sorted,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.32,0:59:18.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,就该请出我们的职业赛车手\N{\fs90}it was time to bring in a racing driver
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.55,0:59:22.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,来试试哪辆车的圈速最快\N{\fs90}to see which of our cars could do the fastest lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.19,0:59:25.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们的常驻美国佬表示对此不感兴趣\N{\fs90}Our resident American said he wasn't interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.51,0:59:28.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这三辆车党性太足\N{\fs90}because all three cars are probably communist.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.80,0:59:32.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我们找了一个比利时佬\N{\fs90}So instead, we went for a Belgian chap-
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.67,0:59:37.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,曾跑过一级方程式和E级方程式\N{\fs90}...who's done Formula One and Formula E,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.34,0:59:39.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,他就是Jerome d'Ambrosio\N{\fs90}Jerome d'Ambrosio.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.81,0:59:46.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了了解每辆车的操控特性\N{\fs90}Jerome took the cars out
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.51,0:59:49.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,Jerome进行了试驾\N{\fs90}to get a sense of how they handled.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.50,1:00:07.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,在他完成之后\N{\fs90}And when he'd finished,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.35,1:00:09.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都想听听\N{\fs90}we were interested to hear
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.26,1:00:11.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,专业人士的意见\N{\fs90}his professional opinion.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.28,1:00:57.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,后来我们才知道\N{\fs90}At this point, word reached us that Jeremy
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.92,1:01:01.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,这段的字幕是杰里米自己瞎配的\N{\fs90}was taking liberties with the subtitling machine.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.95,1:01:05.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以继续我们的壮举\N{\fs90}So we moved on to the big event:
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.96,1:01:08.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,计时赛\N{\fs90}the timed laps.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.93,1:01:15.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,一旦技术人员完成了准备工作\N{\fs90}Once the mechanics had finished their preparations,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.00,1:01:18.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,这三个测速点就会被激活\N{\fs90}the three speed traps were activated.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.37,1:01:25.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,法拉利拉法 在起跑线上\N{\fs90}And the Ferrari LaFerrari took its place
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.08,1:01:27.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,找到了它的位置\N{\fs90}on the start line.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.68,1:01:30.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,看它多漂亮啊\N{\fs90}Look how good it looks there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.72,1:01:34.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,这只是浪费时间 浪费橡胶和汽油\N{\fs90}This is just wasting time. It's wasting rubber and fuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.09,1:01:35.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这就像是开胃小点\N{\fs90}No, this is like an amuse-bouche.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.89,1:01:39.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,是啊 明明已经点了鸭子和雪莉蛋糕\N{\fs90}Yeah, it is. You have ordered the duck and sherry trifle.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.63,1:01:43.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你拿了个蜜瓜球 -我听都没有在听\N{\fs90}- And you're a melon ball. - I'm not even listening.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.94,1:02:03.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们 它现在时速231.4公里\N{\fs90}Gentlemen, it is doing 231.4 kilometers an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.98,1:02:06.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,在直线的尾端\N{\fs90}at the end of the straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.08,1:02:09.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,差不多柴油版高尔夫之类的速度\N{\fs90}It's about the same speed as a Golf diesel, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.34,1:02:26.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,\N{\fs90}194.9.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.77,1:02:28.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,利用重力一路下坡\N{\fs90}Going down the hill using gravity.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.61,1:02:30.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,他停下来去购物了 他肯定的\N{\fs90}- Is he stopping off for shopping? - He must be.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.46,1:02:48.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,他来了\N{\fs90}Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.10,1:02:59.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-詹姆斯 边上风凉去吧 -反正车手热过身了\N{\fs90}- James, if you want to get a cup of tea. - We've warmed the track.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.87,1:03:04.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,下面 该轮到保时捷918出场了\N{\fs90}Next it was the turn of the Porsche 918.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.34,1:03:06.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些条纹会给它的速度加持多少呢\N{\fs90}How much faster will it go because of the stripes?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.88,1:03:08.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,很多\N{\fs90}Much.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.79,1:03:24.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,231点多\N{\fs90}231 point...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.63,1:03:26.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以他比法拉利快\N{\fs90}So he's faster than the Ferrari.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.17,1:03:38.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,\N{\fs90}183.0.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.68,1:03:42.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,比他慢了非常多\N{\fs90}Way, way, way slower than him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.28,1:03:44.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,别忘了在这里和下一个测量点之间\N{\fs90}Don't forget between here and the next measuring point,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.45,1:03:47.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 你还有四个慢速弯道\N{\fs90}Okay, you've got four slow corners,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.09,1:03:49.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,这些就是保时捷将要赶超上来的地方\N{\fs90}and those are the ones where the Porsche is gonna make up time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.66,1:03:52.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为四轮驱动\N{\fs90}Because of the four-wheel steering.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.89,1:03:56.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,像本田披露一样 -不\N{\fs90}- Like a Honda Prelude? - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.14,1:04:12.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,110点什么 1\N{\fs90}- 110 point what? - One.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.94,1:04:16.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 比你快了 0.1\N{\fs90}So, almost to a tenth of a kilometer an hour, the same speed as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.75,1:04:24.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,他来了 他这暴躁的声音\N{\fs90}Here he comes. He's firing noises.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.86,1:04:27.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,在这里 快看那个\N{\fs90}There it is. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.33,1:04:33.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,终于 是精神病人杀手出马了\N{\fs90}Finally, it was the turn of the psycho killer.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.87,1:04:36.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,这三个中最难搞的 最易怒的\N{\fs90}The trickiest, the edgiest of the three.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.04,1:04:39.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是我对它会胜利充满了信心\N{\fs90}But I was so confident it'd win,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.94,1:04:43.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我准备豪赌一把\N{\fs90}I was prepared to take a massive gamble.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.88,1:04:48.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果迈凯伦是最快的\N{\fs90}If the McLaren isn't the fastest,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.70,1:04:52.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们两个可以把我的房子拆了\N{\fs90}you two can knock my house down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.49,1:04:54.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-神马 -把它拆了\N{\fs90}- What? - Knock it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.62,1:04:57.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你的房子 -是的 就是这个意思\N{\fs90}- What, your house? - Yeah, and I mean that.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.49,1:05:01.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是我有多坚定的认为它将会是最快的一个\N{\fs90}That's how confident I am that that will be the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.19,1:05:05.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你知道我们真的干得出来的 -是的\N{\fs90}- You know we will do that? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.33,1:05:07.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这是个严肃的打赌 -是的\N{\fs90}- It's a serious bet? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.77,1:05:10.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好的 -如果它不是最快的\N{\fs90}- Fine. - If that's not the fastest,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.37,1:05:12.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们可以把你的房子拆了 -对哒\N{\fs90}- we can knock your house down? - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.79,1:05:15.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们知道它在哪里 你们都去过\N{\fs90}You know where it is. You've both been.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.17,1:05:17.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,我很愿意把它拆掉\N{\fs90}I'd love to knock it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.52,1:05:25.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们开始吧 这影响很大\N{\fs90}Here we go. A lot riding on this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.33,1:05:41.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,\N{\fs90}235.9.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.80,1:05:44.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 它在第一个直线的末端是最快的\N{\fs90}Okay, it's fastest at the end of the first straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.21,1:05:51.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们愿意来我的家共进晚餐吗\N{\fs90}Would you like to come to my house for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.28,1:05:53.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,好啊 我能带个推土机一起来吗\N{\fs90}Yes. Can I bring a bulldozer?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.82,1:06:02.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,\N{\fs90}188.3.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.69,1:06:04.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,这真是令人心惊的快啊 -利落\N{\fs90}That is worryingly quick. Brisk.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.76,1:06:06.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,这还是挺快的吧\N{\fs90}It's quite brisk?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.56,1:06:09.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们还不知道它急转弯的时候可以开多快呢\N{\fs90}We don't know how fast it's going around the tight turns.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.28,1:06:11.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,也许在那里它只能做到两公里\N{\fs90}Might have been doing two kilometers an hour around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.68,1:06:25.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,他在哪里\N{\fs90}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.43,1:06:27.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,撞车了\N{\fs90}Crashed.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.56,1:06:47.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,随着这个 让我们回到帐篷\N{\fs90}With that, back to the tent.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.31,1:06:57.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们 现在\N{\fs90}Thank you so much. Now...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.14,1:06:59.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要把话说清楚\N{\fs90}I want to make it absolutely plain,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.21,1:07:01.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为这对一些怪胎们很重要\N{\fs90}'cause I know this matters to anoraks,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.21,1:07:06.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有的这三辆车用的都是完全一样的轮胎\N{\fs90}all three cars were running on exactly the same sort of tires.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.69,1:07:09.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 一样的轮胎 一样的赛道 一样的车手\N{\fs90}Yes, same tires, same track, same driver.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.29,1:07:11.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以时间只和车本身相关\N{\fs90}So the times are down to the cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.59,1:07:14.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 而现在是揭晓答案的时候了\N{\fs90}Yup. And now it is time to reveal those times.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.86,1:07:17.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我再说清楚一点\N{\fs90}Let me just make it absolutely clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.06,1:07:18.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们并不知道这些时间\N{\fs90}We don't know what they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.60,1:07:20.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,制作人一直瞒着我们\N{\fs90}The producers have kept them from us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.80,1:07:22.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是顶级机密 -是的\N{\fs90}- They're top secret. - Yup.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.57,1:07:24.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 让我们打开记分板\N{\fs90}So, let's put the scoreboard up,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.30,1:07:25.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们从\N{\fs90}and let's begin with
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.50,1:07:28.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,法拉利拉法开始\N{\fs90}the Ferrari LaFerrari, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.09,1:07:30.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们来看看它做的如何 拜托\N{\fs90}Let's see what it did it in, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.38,1:07:37.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们并不知道这究竟好不好 不是吗\N{\fs90}We don't know if that's any good, do we?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.13,1:07:39.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,接下来让我们看看保时捷\N{\fs90}Let's move on and do the Porsche next.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:39.85,1:07:41.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,保时捷到底开了多快呢\N{\fs90}What did the Porsche do it in?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.69,1:07:46.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊万岁 1:54.2\N{\fs90}Oh, yes! 1:54.2!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.39,1:07:49.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,耶 耶 你看到了吗\N{\fs90}Yes! Yes! You see?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.03,1:07:52.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,你说它会把保时捷碾压成渣\N{\fs90}You said it would mince the Porsche.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.16,1:07:55.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是它并没有 它比保时捷慢\N{\fs90}And it didn't mince it. It was slower than the Porsche.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.57,1:07:57.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,我告诉你了它华而不实\N{\fs90}I told you it's just a melon ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.44,1:07:59.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,它比我的车慢\N{\fs90}It's slower than my car,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.34,1:08:01.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,换种说法比你的车快\N{\fs90}which was faster than your car.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.87,1:08:04.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,0.2秒而已 而且它看上去更好\N{\fs90}0.2 of a second, and it looks better.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.11,1:08:06.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,是 在我后视镜里 还越变越小\N{\fs90}Yeah, it did in my mirror where it belongs getting smaller.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.88,1:08:08.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,它就是华而不实 它输了\N{\fs90}It's a melon ball, and it lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.48,1:08:09.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 -干嘛\N{\fs90}- Hammond. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.68,1:08:11.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,-冷静下来 -好吧\N{\fs90}- Calm down. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.20,1:08:12.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为接下来\N{\fs90}Because now we must bring up
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.74,1:08:15.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,要揭晓真正重要的成绩\N{\fs90}the time that really matters.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.30,1:08:17.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,赌了大价钱了\N{\fs90}The one where a lot's at stake.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.82,1:08:18.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,迈凯伦\N{\fs90}The McLaren...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.93,1:08:19.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,迈凯伦P1\N{\fs90}The McLaren P1.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.96,1:08:22.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你在紧张吗 -没有 -真的 -没有\N{\fs90}- Are you nervous? Sure? - No. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.70,1:08:23.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,-一点点都没有 -没有\N{\fs90}- A little bit? - No!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.00,1:08:25.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,我才没有紧张 -为什么要紧张\N{\fs90}- I'm not nervous. - Why be nervous?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.52,1:08:27.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以拿一辆手推车或者类似的\N{\fs90}You could get, like, a shopping trolley
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.00,1:08:29.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,装上你所有的东西\N{\fs90}and keep all your things in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.20,1:08:32.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,在桥底下交几个新朋友\N{\fs90}Make some new friends under a bridge somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.07,1:08:34.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哈蒙德 -我建议卖器官 但别那样\N{\fs90}- Hammond. - I'd say sell your body but don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.37,1:08:37.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,安静 让我们\N{\fs90}Be quiet! Let's-
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.08,1:08:39.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们把时间给P1 我们开始吧\N{\fs90}Let's bring up the time of the P1. Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.85,1:08:42.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,-哦天哪 -在哪儿\N{\fs90}- Oh, God. - Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.59,1:08:52.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,万岁\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.16,1:09:00.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太逗了 因为你说过\N{\fs90}That is funny. Because you said...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.47,1:09:03.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是最快的 但它不是最快的\N{\fs90}the fastest, but it's not the fastest.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.74,1:09:05.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是最慢的\N{\fs90}It's the slowest!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.70,1:09:08.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们 记者 播音员\N{\fs90}Ladies and gentlemen, journalist, broadcaster
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.98,1:09:12.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,无家可归的人 杰里米 克拉克森\N{\fs90}and homeless man, Jeremy Clarkson.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.28,1:09:24.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是事实 这就是事实\N{\fs90}That's what it is. That's what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.06,1:09:26.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们不会真的把我的房子拆了吧\N{\fs90}You're not really going to knock my house down?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.89,1:09:29.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 我们会的\N{\fs90}Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.36,1:09:31.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,-愿赌服输 -都说定了\N{\fs90}- A bet is a bet. - That's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.40,1:09:34.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我们会录下来 -但是有件事\N{\fs90}- And we're going to film it. - No, but the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.10,1:09:36.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,用迈凯伦自己的轮胎的话\N{\fs90}on the tires that the McLaren can be bought with,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.77,1:09:39.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是最快的\N{\fs90}it was faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.07,1:09:41.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们从刚开始就说好了\N{\fs90}We agreed right at the start
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.51,1:09:43.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们都用一样的轮胎跑\N{\fs90}we'd all run on the same tires.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.88,1:09:46.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,那可是在你的车输掉前就定好的\N{\fs90}That was the deal before your car lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.38,1:09:47.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以让我们\N{\fs90}So let's just...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.88,1:09:51.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,让我们总结一下这第一集 好嘛\N{\fs90}Let's just sum this first show up, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.42,1:09:53.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,我失去了房子\N{\fs90}I've lost my house.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.22,1:09:55.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们和观众打了起来 -而且很惨烈\N{\fs90}- We've had a fight with the audience. - Big one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.62,1:09:58.42,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个人把我们的无人机射了下来\N{\fs90}Somebody shot our drone down.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.46,1:10:01.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我们杀了三个大名人\N{\fs90}And we've killed three quite major celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.19,1:10:03.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 乐观点讲\N{\fs90}Yeah, but on the plus side,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.33,1:10:05.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,我保时捷是最快的\N{\fs90}my Porsche was the fastest!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.90,1:10:13.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,伴随着这个糟糕的失望之情\N{\fs90}And on that terrible disappointment,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.11,1:10:15.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想是结束的时候了\N{\fs90}I'm afraid it's time to end.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.17,1:10:17.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,十分感谢你们的到来\N{\fs90}Thank you all very much for coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.01,1:10:18.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢你们的收看\N{\fs90}Thank you for watching.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.51,1:10:20.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,下礼拜我们在约翰内斯堡再见\N{\fs90}And we'll see you next week in Johannesburg.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.41,1:10:22.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs90}Good-bye!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.41,1:10:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
